                            <comment id="13629138" author="davsclaus" created="Thu, 11 Apr 2013 17:27:22 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Thanks for reporting.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Are you considering working on a patch?&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="13629963" author="mdo" created="Fri, 12 Apr 2013 10:08:26 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Hello Claus, yes I&apos;d do, but I see it was already fixed in trunk by Willem. Thanks!&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="13631552" author="bvahdat" created="Mon, 15 Apr 2013 07:24:07 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Willem, not an issue at all, but IMHO instead of:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;IOHelper.close(is, &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;null&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;null&lt;/span&gt;);
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;We could probably better do:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;IOHelper.close(is, &lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;pom.properties&quot;&lt;/span&gt;, LOG);
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Or the shortest way of it if you would prefer:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;IOHelper.close(is);
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="13631558" author="njiang" created="Mon, 15 Apr 2013 07:30:18 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Hi, Babak&lt;br/&gt;
Yeah, it makes sense. &lt;br/&gt;
I will updated the code for it.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
